Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:24.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈·克洛斯羅德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.11,0:19:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊恩先生讓我把這機體帶給你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:30.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對接吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:31.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
